version_description: Throw on some shades and hit the beach in a new seasonal Playground with Summer avatars!
Maxwell and Lily are dressed up and trick or treating in this spooky Halloween update featuring all-new Mummy, Pirate, and Zombie avatars and a pumpkin-filled playground. Trick or treat!
Fall is here and Pilgrim Maxwell and Lily are ready to feast!  Enjoy an all new fall themed playground as well as new playable avatars Cornucopia, Pumpkin Prince, and Gobbles!

Run run as fast as you can, you can’t catch him…actually you probably can…he’s the partially eaten Gingerbread Man! Celebrate the holidays with a brand new holiday themed playground and new, playable holiday avatars!
